Adds a keyboard shortcut to swap the windows tiled to the left and right halves of the screen.

To set the shortcut to trigger the action: go to [i]System Settings[/i] > [i]Shortcuts[/i] > search for [i]Swap Left and Right[/i] > set your preferred shortcut.

For more information on installation as well as any requests, please visit [url=https://github.com/nclarius/KWin-window-positioning-scripts/tree/main/swap-left-right]the GitHub page[/url].

